name: Electric platformer
body:
### Electric Platformer

This is the webpage for Electric Platformer, a COS 426 final project by Brent Read and Steven Lyubromirsky. It seeks to simulate electric forces in a platformer. A narrated walkthrough of the game can be found [here](https://youtu.be/ev-BGC7_CxA)
